data.description: Adorable, move-in ready! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home has a gas fireplace with updated mantel and no direct back neighbors. There are a generous amount of upgrades with a farmhouse feel. The entryway is tile and leads into a spacious family/living area. Kitchen includes tile flooring, lovely cabinetry and backsplash. Dining area has access to the large back deck; a perfect location for grilling. Primary bedroom includes a dedicated attached bathroom along with lovely barn doors. You will truly enjoy the amazing touches and style of this home. Minutes away from I25, Fort Carson, and Powers Corridor.  Heritage Subdivision includes parks and attaches to walking trails. **ASSUMABLE LOW % RATE**
